briefTitle: Study to Investigate Immunogenicity, Efficacy and Safety of Treatment With Human-cl rhFVIII
officialTitle: Extension Study for Patients Who Completed GENA-05 (NuProtect)- to Investigate Immunogenicity, Efficacy and Safety of Treatment With Human-cl rhFVIII
summary: The purpose of the study is to collect long-term data on the inhibitor development rate of Human-cl rhFVIII in previously untreated patients with severe Hemophilia A.

primaryOutcome.measure: Immunogenicity of Human-cl rhFVIII: Incidence of Inhibitors
